INSERT INTO `main_site_service` VALUES (1,'Home Consultation','M','fa-comments','A good chat about your dreams and hopes for the project and a discussion of your design ideas\r\nA look through some specially chosen samples to discover your interiors taste\r\nA site survey with measurements and photographs taken\r\nAdvice on the practicalities of making design changes','£110 per room for a 2 hour consultation (plus travel over a 10 mile radius)',1,0),(2,'Interior Design','M','fa-pencil-alt','Full layout planning with a scale floor plan\r\nColour schemes, window and flooring treatments, furniture, lighting and accessories all handpicked for you\r\nA sample board so that you can see how all the items in your design work together\r\nVisualisations using Sketch Up Pro so you can see how your room will look\r\nA Full breakdown of costs and a list of all items in your design so that you can choose to buy yourself','£55 per hour or a day rate of £300 (8 hours @ £37.50)',2,0),(3,'Procurement','M','fa-truck','Make one convenient payment and I will order everything for you\r\nI create an ordering schedule and book deliveries so that items arrive on time for installation\r\nI organise any returns or exchanges, making the process stress free\r\nAs I\'m not tied to any suppliers I can source items from anywhere, making sure you get the look you want at the best prices\r\nYou get access to my trade discounts which range from 10%-40%','A handling charge of 15% of the retail cost of the goods',3,0),(4,'Installation Management','M','fa-paint-roller','I can help you as much or as little as you like, choose from the following services:\r\nCoordination and supervision of all trades to ensure your project is finished to a high standard\r\nRegular site visits to supervise trades and check on progress\r\nOn site problem solving to make sure your project runs smoothly\r\nOverseeing the final touches - pictures placed correctly, cushions plumped and all accessories styled perfectly','£55 per hour or a day rate of £300 (8 hours @ £37.50)',4,0),(5,'Free introductory phone call','O','fa-phone-volume','Have a project in mind but not sure what\'s involved? \r\nNot sure if you need an interior designer? \r\nWhy not have a no obligation chat with me about your project? \r\nLet me know what you\'re thinking of doing, and I can give you an idea of the steps you\'ll need to take your project from wishlist to finished room. A chance to get to know me a little before deciding if you\'d like to work with me','Free 15 minute call',5,0),(6,'Online interior design','O','fa-desktop','Don\'t live in the area?\r\nWould you prefer to work over email? I can still help you!\r\nFill out my simple questionnaire, and we can design your room completely online.\r\nI\'ve worked with clients as far afield as London, Dubai and the Cayman Islands, always with fab results and happy clients.\r\nIncludes 2D visualisations so that you can picture how your new room will look','£400 per room',6,0),(7,'Smaller projects','O','fa-cut','Don\'t need an entire room redesign?\r\nDo you have a smaller project in mind? \r\nIf you just need help to choose a wall colour or new window dressings for example, then I can help you. \r\nIf you are in the planning stages of a project and would like some advice before beginning work, or just feel that a fixed fee design package might not work for you, then please get in touch and I will be happy to discuss your project with you and agree a fee structure.','£55 per hour or a day rate of £300 (8 hours @ £37.50)',7,0),(8,'Interior styling','O','fa-couch','Are you selling or letting a property?\r\nOr just need help to make the most of what you already have?\r\nWould you like to increase your chances of selling or attracting the perfect tenant? \r\nI can help with styling, decluttering and staging your home so that it looks its best, as a well presented home not only sells more quickly, it can boost the purchase price or rental income','£55 per hour or a day rate of £300 (8 hours @ £37.50)',8,0);
