INSERT INTO `main_site_siteconfig` VALUES (1,'https://www.instagram.com/louise_m_interiors/','https://www.facebook.com/louise.m.interiors/','https://www.houzz.co.uk/pro/louiseminteriors','https://uk.linkedin.com/in/louise-misell-409261105','https://www.pinterest.co.uk/louisemisell/','13 Pen-y-lan Terrace\r\nPenylan\r\nCardiff\r\nCF23 9EU','louise@louisemisellinteriors.co.uk','+447811287791','+442920497667','Privacy_Policy.pdf','Terms_and_Conditions_2_g25GXNj.pdf',4000,10000,'https://twitter.com/l_m_interiors','The latest news, tips and interiors inspiration from Louise Misell Interiors. See my posts about anything from the latest fabric and wallpaper collections to \'how to\' guides for all things interiors related.','Here you can find my contact details or send me a message. You can book an introductory telephone call with me or make a home consultation appointment using the online booking form. I look forward to hearing from you.','I\'m a Cardiff based interior designer, offering a full range of design services with clear pricing. I have designed hundreds of unique room schemes for a wide range of clients and budgets for people across South Wales, including city apartments, holiday rentals and large rural properties.','The design schemes I have produced are varied and bespoke to each client, as I work with you to create an interior which reflects your personality. Have a look at my portfolio to see the range of my work.','Here are the interior design services I offer, from help with a small project to a full design with project management. I operate on a fixed fee or hourly rate basis, with all my prices clearly marked. I can give you as much or as little help as you\'d like, and will tailor my service to your needs.','See what some of my satisfied clients have to say about their experience of working with me, and how I helped them transform their homes in to space which work practically, and which they love to spend time in.','Who is Louise Misell? Find out all about me - who I am, my education and background, my interior design training, and the reason why I set up my interior design business.','About Louise Misell','The latest news, tips and inspiration from Louise Misell Interiors','Welcome to my design blog, where you\'ll see posts about anything from my current interiors obsession, the latest fabric and wallpaper collections and \'how to\' guides for all things interiors related. I love colour and mixing pattern, but also covet an uncluttered interiors look. I especially love the moment when you see something so beautiful that it makes you take a sharp intake of breath. Happy reading, and if you have any questions, would like to chat about anything interiors related, or share your interiors obsession, please use the contact form to get in touch. \r\n\r\nThank you, \r\n\r\nLouise','Design insider - news, tips and inspiration','My contact details and how to book','Welcome to Louise Misell Interiors','I offer a full range of interior design services and can help with anything from choosing paint colours to a complete redesign of your home or commercial space. I specialise in space planning to make your interiors work practically for you, and will work with you to help you define your interiors style. I come to you and will travel across South Wales including Cardiff, Swansea, Newport, Penarth, Cowbridge, The Vale of Glamorgan and surrounding areas.','Inspiring interior design for real people','The design schemes I have produced are varied and bespoke to each client, as I don’t have a signature design style but work with you to create an interior which reflects your personality. Please take a look at my portfolio to see the range of my work, and the many different styles of interiors which I can create.','My interior design portfolio','I offer a full range of interior design services, and can help you as much or as little as you like. I can come to your home to give you interior design advice as a one off appointment, or if you\'d like more help, I can design your room scheme for you. You can then choose to order items from the scheme yourself, or I can order for you and arrange delivery of your items. If you need some help with finding tradespeople to carry out any work needed, from hanging pictures to building bespoke bookshelves, I can call in trusted tradespeople to do the work for you. I have an ever growing list of professional tradespeople I have worked with who I can recommend, and I can also coordinate and supervise them to make sure the work is completed to your satisfaction. I work with a local seamstress who makes beautiful bespoke curtains and blinds, and have trained curtain fitters who can install your curtain tracks or poles, and hang your curtains for you. I operate on a fixed fee or an hourly rate basis, and all my prices are clearly marked, as I believe that in order to budget well, you need to know what your project is going to cost you.','The interior design services I offer','Customer service is a top priority for me, as I want the whole experience to be enjoyable and as stress free as possible from start to finish. Scroll down to see what some of my satisfied clients have to say about working with me, and how I helped them transform their homes into spaces which they love to spend time in. Some of these homes have been featured on my portfolio page, click on \'see project\' to see the before and after pictures, and to read the story of their transformations.','Reviews of my work with customers','£110-£600','https://www.homify.co.uk/professionals/5749220/louise-misell-interiors','https://www.bark.com/en/company/louiselouisemisellinteriorscouk/aggmo/','{\"token\": \"EAAgDIOQeURcBAIh9kqZANN9ZBLrIOhZCZCDuL6YQZA52rxMTZAhPlqhWqfOgi8IfyuYzZBEW879UI3jCZCwWRZCReQ6h7fdkEGAQMZCv4TcfGTEh2yZB0nQEOOStFkn43CYdW0IRVmMOMbPbxCqZBw5yeKMd2iEk1Tan9l4ZD\"}','164508254214036');
